    <p>{`In any case we were able to see the coronoation chair that has been used to crown the kings and queens of England for many centuries, the resting place of such kings and queens such as Queen Elizabeth, the alter floor that the cornations take place, and Prince William and Kates wedding took place, as well as the chapel behind the alter that the royal family disappeared to during the ceremony to sign the marriage documents away from the camera’s. (This is the resting place of several Kings and Queens).`}</p>
